   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Human Rights Education in Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will select 28 teachers from 28 secondary schools in the Niger Delta region of Nigeria to be trained in Peace,Safety and Human Rights programs that will be implemented by the teachers in their various schools.This will improve peace,safety and human rights of the people.The youth of Niger Delta have become the instrument used to perpetrate violence and many of them have lost their lives.The project will translate 5,000 young people into peace builders and human rights advocate.</narrative>
  </description>
